      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIC BOCCA (5) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts three wins and three placings. Recorded a 4.5 lengths win (25.18) in a Restricted WIN H last time at this track. Expected to go close. FLYING OFFSHORE (1) finished fourth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 450m at this track, taking a Bottom Up - Grade 6 in a handy 25.34. Has the ability and looks a key chance. ONYX LASS (4) has a strong record here with two wins and a minor from five starts. Recorded a 0.8 lengths win (25.40) in a Restricted WIN H last time at this track. Suited here and expected to run well. KAELIX STORM (3) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
